<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Terra do Amanhã | Agronegócio Sustentável</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-stone-50 text-stone-900 transition-colors duration-300">

    <div id="accessibility-hub" class="fixed bottom-6 right-6 z-50 bg-white/90 dark:bg-stone-900/90 backdrop-blur-md p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800 transition-all duration-300 transform translate-y-0">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3 border-b border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800 pb-2">
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide text-stone-700 dark:text-stone-300">Acessibilidade</h3>
            <button id="toggle-hub" class="text-xs text-stone-400 hover:text-stone-600">Minimizar</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
                <label class="block text-xs text-stone-500 mb-1">Tamanho do Texto</label>
                <div class="flex gap-2">
                    <button id="font-dec" class="px-3 py-1 bg-stone-100 dark:bg-stone-800 rounded font-bold hover:bg-stone-200 text-xs">- A</button>
                    <button id="font-res" class="px-3 py-1 bg-stone-100 dark:bg-stone-800 rounded font-bold hover:bg-stone-200 text-xs">Reset</button>
                    <button id="font-inc" class="px-3 py-1 bg-stone-100 dark:bg-stone-800 rounded font-bold hover:bg-stone-200 text-xs">+ A</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-xs text-stone-500">Contraste Escuro</span>
                <button id="toggle-dark" class="w-10 h-6 bg-stone-200 dark:bg-emerald-600 rounded-full relative transition-colors duration-300">
                    <span class="absolute top-1 left-1 bg-white w-4 h-4 rounded-full transition-transform duration-300 dark:translate-x-4"></span>
                </button>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-xs text-stone-500">Ouvir Texto</span>
                <button id="btn-tts" class="bg-emerald-700 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded text-xs hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors">
                    ▶ Play
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <header class="min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-between p-6 md:p-12 border-b border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center w-full">
            <span class="font-serif italic text-xl tracking-wider text-emerald-800 dark:text-emerald-400">Terra do Amanhã.</span>
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400">Edição 2026</span>
        </div>

        <main class="my-auto max-w-4xl section-voice">
            <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-8xl font-normal leading-none tracking-tight mb-6">
                O futuro da <br><span class="italic text-emerald-800 dark:text-emerald-400">agricultura</span> é consciente.
            </h1>
            <p class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 max-w-xl font-light leading-relaxed">
                Unindo tecnologia de precisão e respeito ao solo para alimentar as próximas gerações sem esgotar o presente.
            </p>
        </main>

        <div class="flex justify-between items-end w-full text-xs text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-wider">
            <span>Scroll para explorar</span>
            <span>01 / 03</span>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="reveal-section min-h-screen grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 border-b border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
        <div class="p-6 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center section-voice">
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 font-bold mb-4">Tecnologia Aplicada</span>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl mb-6">Dados que nutrem a terra</h2>
            <p class="font-sans text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Através de sensores IoT e inteligência artificial, conseguimos mapear a saúde do solo em tempo real. Isso reduz o uso de água em até 40% e elimina o desperdício de insumos químicos.
            </p>
            <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-emerald-700 pl-4 italic font-serif text-stone-500">
                "A tecnologia não veio para substituir a natureza, mas para decifrar suas necessidades."
            </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-200 min-h-[300px] md:min-h-full bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560493450-b147986c50bc?q=80&w=1000');">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="reveal-section min-h-screen grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="bg-stone-200 min-h-[300px] md:min-h-full bg-cover bg-center order-2 md:order-1" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550751827-4bd374c3f58b?q=80&w=1000');">
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center order-1 md:order-2 section-voice">
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 font-bold mb-4">Inclusão Digital</span>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl mb-6">Informação acessível para todos</h2>
            <p class="font-sans text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
                Acreditamos que o conhecimento sobre sustentabilidade deve ser universal. Esta plataforma foi desenhada seguindo as diretrizes do WCAG, garantindo que pessoas com deficiências visuais ou motoras consumam o conteúdo com total autonomia através do nosso painel nativo.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
